array.name: bootloader
array.string:
SEND,mtdparts default\n\p
nand erase.part rootfs0\n\p\p\p\p
nand erase.part rootfs1\n
,erase,,,0,1,

array.name: debian
array.string: SEND,#qemu-system-i386 -curses -boot d -cdrom output/images/rootfs.iso9660 -m 512\\n\r\nqemu-system-arm -machine vexpress-a9 -nographic -no-reboot -kernel output/build/uboot-2019.07/u-boot \\n,buildroot qemu,,,0,1,
SEND,cd $PRJROOT/zebos/platform/linux\\r\\n\r\nmake clean-vrrpd && rm -rf obj/vrrpd/ && make vrrpd \\n\r\ncd - \\n,remake vrrpd,,,0,1,

array.name: Default
array.string:
SEND,end\r\n
conf t\r\n
management vlan 1 ip address 192.168.1.92/24 gateway 192.168.1.1\r\n
end\r\n
ifconfig eth0 192.168.1.92 \r\n,ip,,,0,1,

SEND,end\r\n
no debug dot1x all \r\n
no ethernet cfm debug erps\r\n
no ethernet cfm debug event\r\n
no ethernet cfm debug rx\r\n
no ethernet cfm debug tx\r\n
undebug erps\r\n
no debug hsl pkt\r\n
no debug hsl server\r\n
no debug mstp all\r\n
no debug nsm all\r\n
no debug igmp snooping all \r\n
no diagnostic oam enable \r\n
conf t\r\n
no debug dot1x all \r\n
no debug igmp snooping all \r\n
no debug nsm all\r\n
no debug mstp all\r\n
logg con 6\r\n
no logg level all\r\n,undebug,,,0,1,

SEND,end\r\n
#debug dot1x all \r\n
#debug erps\r\n
#ethernet cfm debug erps\r\n
#ethernet cfm debug event\r\n
#ethernet cfm debug rx\r\n
#ethernet cfm debug tx\r\n
#debug hsl pkt\r\n
#debug hsl server\r\n
#debug mstp all\r\n
#debug nsm all\r\n
debug igmp snooping all \r\n
#diagnostic oam enable \r\n
conf t\r\n
#debug dot1x all \r\n
debug igmp snooping all \r\n
#debug nsm all\r\n
#debug mstp all\r\n
logg con 7\r\n
#logg lev auth 7\r\n
logg le l2mrib 7\r\n
#logg le nsm 7\r\n
#logg le mstp 7\r\n
#logg le hsl 7\r\n
#logg le onm 7\r\n,debug,,,0,1,

SEND,end\r\n
show spanning-tree | include tate\r\n \r\n
#show spanning-tree mst instance 2 | include tate\r\n
show diagnostic stp status \r\n
show diagnostic stp instance 0\r\n
#show diagnostic stp instance 1\r\n
#show diagnostic stp instance 2\r\n
,show mstp,,,0,1,
SEND,end \\r\\n\r\nshow igmp snooping all \\r\\n \r\nshow diagnostic igmp \\r\\n,show igmp,,,0,1,
SEND,debug trace module level erps * none\\n\r\ndebug trace module level mep * none\\n\r\nplatform debug deny \\n,vtss undbg,,,0,1,
SEND,end\\n entershell\\n\r\nwget http://192.168.1.106/bin/vrrpd && chmod 777 vrrpd && mv vrrpd /usr/bin/ && reboot \\n,wget vrrpd,,,0,1,

array.name: script
array.string: SEND,rm -rf output/*/ && rm -rf output/*.done\\n\\p\r\ntree output/ \\n,build data,,,0,1,

array.name: UTP
array.string:
SEND,\n
admin\n\p
admin\n\p
enable\n
quit_hl\n\p\n
alias nget="nvram get"\n
alias nset="nvram set"\n
alias nsave="nvram commit"\n,login,,,0,1,

SEND,end\r\n
conf t\r\n
management vlan 1 ip address 192.168.1.92/24 gateway 192.168.1.1\r\n
end\r\n
ifconfig eth0 192.168.1.92 \r\n,ip,,,0,1,
SEND,nvram get erps_stg\\n\\p\r\nnvram set erps_cmd="show_stg;1;9"\\n\\p\r\nnvram set erps_cmd="show_stg;1;10"\\n\\p,show stg,,,0,1,

SEND,ps | grep erps | grep -v grep | awk '{print $1}' | xargs kill \n
cd /tmp/\n
ftpget -u admin -p admin 2.2.2.2 erps erps\r\n
ftpget -u admin -p admin 2.2.2.2 msgdump msgdump \r\n
chmod 777 erps msgdump\r\n
./erps &\r\n,ftpget,,,0,1,

SEND,ps | grep erps | grep -v grep | awk '{print $1}' | xargs kill \n
cd /tmp/\n
ftpget -u admin -p admin 192.168.100.106 erps erps\r\n
ftpget -u admin -p admin 192.168.100.106 msgdump msgdump \r\n
chmod 777 erps msgdump\r\n
./erps&\r\n,ftpget2,,,0,1,
SEND,ps | grep erps | grep -v grep | awk '{print $1}' | xargs kill \\n,pkill erps,,,0,1,
SEND,ps | grep erps | grep -v grep | awk '{print $1}' | xargs kill \\n\r\n./erps&\\n,restart erps,,,0,1,
SEND,nvram get erps_stg && nvram get erps_ring && nvram get erps_inst \\n,dumpcfg,,,0,1,
